<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Every sub-section of the widget selection contains widgets that fulfil a very specific purpose. You add widgets to the page by clicking on a widget in the selection and dragging it onto the body area (5). You can find a list of all widgets and their settings below.</p></td>
